beer.beer_description: May Contain Traces Of Panther is a bit of a hybrid. It's more of a traditional British Porter insofar as it isn't black, it's a very dark red, and more caramelly than it is roasty. Taking some more modern cues on hop aroma and ABV, this sessionable 6.2% malt fest is a warm and cuddly snugglepuss, but can get a little dangerous.
